h3 Slider Widget
p
    | The Slider Widget wraps the excellent 
    a(href='https://refreshless.com/nouislider/', target="_blank") noUiSlider
    |  library to create a time range slider.
    | For the most part, all features available in noUiSlider
    | can be used in this widget.

h4 Properties
p.
    These are the properties specific to this widget.  
    General Cyclotron widget properties are not repeated here (e.g. layout properties).

property-table(properties='config.widgets.slider.properties')

h4 Min and max value
p
    | These properties indicate the range of the time slider. They must have the same valid moment.js format, which can be specified in 
    em momentFormat 
    | property.

h4 Player
p.
    Player property specifies an optional play/pause button that will cause the slider to slide automatically after each interval of the specified length. 
    The button is displayed before (if horizontal) or on top of the slider (if vertical).

property-table(properties='config.widgets.slider.properties.player.properties')

h4 Pips
p.
    Points shown along the slider. More details and examples are provided in the noUiSlider documentation.

p.
    Mode property configures the way pips are displayed.
ul
    li Range mode places a pip for every point specified in the range.
    li Steps mode places a pip for every step.
    li Positions mode places pips at percentage-based positions (percentages can be specified in Values option).
    li Count mode generates a fixed number of pips (specified in Values option).
    li Values mode is the same as Positions mode but with values instead of percentages.

property-table(properties='config.widgets.slider.properties.pips.properties')

